You know, I've made fun of ICP relentlessly over the years. They and their fans have always been a good standby joke, really even just invoking their names brought laughter and smiles to my friends and I. Now that﻿ I'm a little older I think I can finally say - ICP are legit clowns. That's a complete compliment. I cracked up at this video and find their interviews refreshingly candid. I have never and will never like their music, but they've made a dynasty for themselves. ICP is cool in my book.
